span></span></label><div class='gfield_description' id='gfield_description_93_10'>What&#8217;s Your Email</div><div class='ginput_container ginput_container_email'>\n                            <input name='input_10' id='input_93_10' type='email' value='' class='medium'    aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" aria-describedby=\"gfield_description_93_10\" />\n                        </div></li></ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class='gform-page-footer gform_page_footer top_label'>\n                         <input type='button' id='gform_next_button_93_6' class='gform_next_button gform-theme-button button' onclick='gform.submission.handleButtonClick(this);' data-submission-type='next' value='Next'  /> \n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div id='gform_page_93_2' class='gform_page' data-js='page-field-id-6' style='display:none;'>\n                    <div class='gform_page_fields'>\n                        <ul id='gform_fields_93_2' class='gform_fields top_label form_sublabel_below description_above validation_below'><li id=\"field_93_2\" class=\"gfield gfield--type-text field_sublabel_below gfield--has-description field_description_above field_validation_below gfield_visibility_visible\"  ><label class='gfield_label gform-field-label' for='input_93_2'>What&#039;s The Name Of The Team That You Will Play On</label><div class='gfield_description' id='gfield_description_93_2'>Enter A Team Name. You Can Change This At Any Time Prior To The Start Of The Season. Only One Submission Per Team Is Required</div><div class='ginput_container ginput_container_text'><input name='input_2' id='input_93_2' type='text' value='' class='large'  aria-describedby=\"gfield_description_93_2\"    aria-invalid=\"false\"   /></div></li><li id=\"field_93_3\" class=\"gfield gfield--type-textarea field_sublabel_below gfield--no-description field_description_above field_validation_below gfield_visibility_visible\"  ><label class='g